    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty \u2013 it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it is honestly in pristine, flawless condition. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner incredibly happy. Drop me a message and come take a look!",
