    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage, preserving the deep, glass-like luster of its original factory paint, which is free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the 'new car' scent is remarkably still present. Every button, switch, and technological feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented from day one with only genuine parts used. It has been treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating and has never been exposed to inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine, investment-quality example for the most discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
