      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it's in such spectacular shape that it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and it's been kept in truly pristine condition. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
